Installation of OWASP Juice shop In Kali Linux for Security Assessment 

Operation System : Kali Linux 
Tool Used - Docker 

Installation 
Step 1- Google "Github Owasp Juice Shop"
Step 2- Update the kali with these commands 
      2.1 sudo apt update 
      2.2 sudo apt install docker.io
Step 3- docker pull bkimminich/juice-shop
Step 4- docker run --rm -p 127.0.0.1:3000:3000 bkimminich/juice shop
Step 5- Go to the browser and type - localhost:3000
![Insatlled](Screenshots\Successfully installed.png)